article_title: Israeli military casualties in Jabalia refugee camp, says Hamas military wing.
sentence: The  Izzedine  al-Qassam  Brigades,  which  is  the  military  wing  of  Hamas,  says  it  has  killed  Israeli  troops  there  with  "high-explosive  materials"  In  a  statement  on  messaging  app  Telegram,  the  group  says  its  fighters  saw  the  arrival  of  "a  tank,  an  armoured  personnel  carrier,  and  two  'D9'  military  bulldozers"  loaded  with  explosives.
